data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with 2 car garage in Princeton Manor community on a low maintenance LARGE CORNER LOT with an OPEN FLOOR PLAN and partial WATER VIEWS! Clean, freshly painted inside, meticulously maintained home has all laminate flooring and high ceilings offering plenty of natural light throughout. Great use of space for daily living and entertaining friends and family. Features modern cabinetry with abundant storage, breakfast area and separate dining room, a large living room, breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, spotlights, new ceiling fans, and a laundry room. Split bedroom plan offers a large master bedroom with a private bath and shower & built-in walk-in closet with plenty of storage space. The other bedrooms and bathroom are located on the other side of the home. Through the sliding doors, there is an open deck leading to the large backyard - perfect for weekend cookouts or enjoying your morning coffee with water views. With this easily-¬to-¬maintain yard: add private fencing, pool or a playground area ¬- it's only up to your imagination to create your dream backyard! Low HOA fees. Easy and quick access to I-4 and all the stores, shopping, and restaurants!! This home is a must-see!
